2.10	The_Compton_School	The Compton School	The Compton School is situated on Summers Lane, North Finchley, London. It is an academy school for boys and girls aged eleven to sixteen and the school years range from year 7 to year 11. It is located on the site of Finchley Manorhill School, which was progressively closed in the late 1980s. The buildings were reopened as The Compton School in 1992.	
